.TH GLwDrawingAreaMakeCurrent 3X "" "" "" ""
.SH NAME
\fBGLwDrawingAreaMakeCurrent \(em Make the current GLwDrawingArea current.\fP
.iX "GLwDrawingAreaMakeCurrent""
.iX "GLwDrawingArea"
.sp 1
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fB#include <X11/GLw/GLwDraw.h>\fP
.br
\fBvoid GLwDrawingAreaMakeCurrent(w, ctx)\fP
.br
.ta .5i 1.5i
	Widget \fIw\fP;
.br
	GLXContext \fIctx\fP;
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBGLwDrawingAreaMakeCurrent\fP is a front end to \fIglXMakeCurrent\fP,
however instead of passing in a Display and a Window, a Widget is
passed in.
.SH RELATED INFORMATION
\fBGLwMDrawingArea\fP, \fBglXMakeCurrent\fP.
